data.title: Schubert Songs
data.text: The following discography of Schubert song on 78rpm disc was compiled by Karsten Lehl, who has kindly allowed us to reproduce it here. The entries are arranged by Deutsch number (after the catalogue of Schubert Lieder compiled by Otto Deutsch). An alphabetical list of song titles with Deutsch numbers, suitable for cross-reference, is available at http://www.recmusic.org/lieder/s/schubert.html. Under each title, the second name given is that of the accompanist: where only the instrument name is given, the identity of the accompanist is unknown. Data are not always available for every field.
